{"word":"παραφρονέω","slug":"παραφρονέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>παραφρονέω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:παράφρων'><el>παράφρων</el></a>\n<p/><i>to be beside oneself, be deranged</i> or <i>mad</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; <a href='S:poetically'>poet.</a> <el>παραιφρ-</el>, <b><a href='S:Theocritus'>Theocr.</a></b><p/>"}]}